FGT_config.value:
diag sys ha hadiff log enable
diag debug app hasync -1
diag debug enable
config system dns
 unset primary
    unset secondary
 end
 config system auto-scale
     set status enable
     set sync-interface port1
 set role master
     set callback-url ${CALLBACK_URL}
     set psksecret 12345678
 end
 config system global
     set admin-sport 8443
 end
 config system interface
     edit port1
        set description ext
     next
     edit port2
        set description int
        set mode dhcp
        set defaultgw disable
     next
 end
